[list]
[*] [b]X4: Foundations[/b]: Version [b]8.00[/b] or higher.
[*] [b]UI Extensions and HUD[/b]: Version 8.04 or higher by [url=https://next.nexusmods.com/profile/kuertee?gameId=2659]kuertee[/url].
[list]
